  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A Short PSX Psychological Horror</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You find yourself stranded in a forest after your car breaks down.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2994800/extras/3092850756480f1038ddee8647c32bae.avif?t=1771719765\" width=600 height=374 /></span><strong>would you like to come in, for a call? </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2994800/extras/cad0987189f9459284a8cf5945ee5133.poster.avif?t=1771719765\" width=600 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2994800/extras/cad0987189f9459284a8cf5945ee5133.webm?t=1771719765\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Immerse yourself in a haunting PSX-style retro world, or will it consume you?. </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>'Psychological' Horror:</strong> Immerse yourself in a PSX-style horror experience that delves deep into the psyche. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Interactive Dialogues:</strong> Multiple dialogue choices.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Story-Driven</strong>: Focused heavily on narrative.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Multilingual Support:</strong> Enjoy the game in your preferred language with subtitle support for 15 different languages.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Beautiful Soundtrack:</strong> Experience an evocative and atmospheric soundtrack.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Short & Perfect for a Weekend:</strong> Designed to be completed over a single session in a weekend, offering a concise yet impactful experience.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Achievements:</strong> Unlock a full set of achievements, adding an extra layer of challenge and replayability.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Atmospheric:</strong> The game creates a deeply immersive atmosphere that captivates and unsettles, making every moment memorable.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Room for speculation</strong>: The story and dialogues are designed to provoke  thoughts and speculation, leaving room for interpretation and personal reflection.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Controls:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    WASD for movement</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    Shift for fast walk</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    E / controller for interaction</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    Space or Enter for dialogue</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    Arrow keys / controller to move between dialogues</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A Short PSX Psychological Horror</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You find yourself stranded in a forest after your car breaks down.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2994800/extras/3092850756480f1038ddee8647c32bae.avif?t=1771719765\" width=600 height=374 /></span><strong>would you like to come in, for a call? </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2994800/extras/cad0987189f9459284a8cf5945ee5133.poster.avif?t=1771719765\" width=600 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2994800/extras/cad0987189f9459284a8cf5945ee5133.webm?t=1771719765\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Immerse yourself in a haunting PSX-style retro world, or will it consume you?. </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>'Psychological' Horror:</strong> Immerse yourself in a PSX-style horror experience that delves deep into the psyche. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Interactive Dialogues:</strong> Multiple dialogue choices.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Story-Driven</strong>: Focused heavily on narrative.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Multilingual Support:</strong> Enjoy the game in your preferred language with subtitle support for 15 different languages.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Beautiful Soundtrack:</strong> Experience an evocative and atmospheric soundtrack.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Short & Perfect for a Weekend:</strong> Designed to be completed over a single session in a weekend, offering a concise yet impactful experience.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Achievements:</strong> Unlock a full set of achievements, adding an extra layer of challenge and replayability.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Atmospheric:</strong> The game creates a deeply immersive atmosphere that captivates and unsettles, making every moment memorable.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Room for speculation</strong>: The story and dialogues are designed to provoke  thoughts and speculation, leaving room for interpretation and personal reflection.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Controls:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    WASD for movement</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    Shift for fast walk</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    E / controller for interaction</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    Space or Enter for dialogue</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    Arrow keys / controller to move between dialogues</p></li></ul>",
